fg_segments: Click the image below to confirm our Better Business Bureau membership:
Established in 1995 WriteExpress Corporation has been selling software since 1997.
We strive to please all our customers. WriteExpress does not send spam or sell email addresses.
What information do you collect and how do you use it?
When placing a CD order, you will be asked to fill out and submit an online form that includes your name, telephone number, mailing address, e-mail address and credit card information.
WriteExpress uses two highly reputable, secure stores to sell its products online.
Both have their own privacy policies: Third-Party Web Beacons:
We use Google Analytics to help analyze where visitors go and what they do while visiting our website.

Yahoo! may also use anonymous information about your visits to this and other websites in order to improve its products and services and provide advertisements about goods and services of interest to you.
If you would like more information about this practice and to know your choices about not having this information used by Yahoo!, click here.
Is my order secure? Security for buyers when ordering through a Yahoo! Store

How do you protect my email address? To continuously assess the value of our online shopping experience, we may track the way customers use our site; however, this information is analyzed only in the aggregate and not at the individual level.
WriteExpress Corporation has a strong history of providing excellent customer service, and our goal is to continue this tradition.
With your permission, from time to time, we may notify you of special offers and/or send you online information that may be of interest to you. We look forward to serving you.

WriteExpress Corporation has been selling software since 1997. We strive to please all our customers.
WriteExpress does not send spam or sell email addresses.

What information do you collect and how do you use it?
When placing a CD order, you will be asked to fill out and submit an online form that includes your name, telephone number, mailing address, e-mail address and credit card information. WriteExpress uses two highly reputable, secure stores to sell its products online. Both have their own privacy policies:
            
Third-Party Web Beacons: We use Google Analytics to help analyze where visitors go and what they do while visiting our website. We look forward to serving you.
